  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 415184e09ccc2df40ae7ff9b23a0cc8d, type: 3}
  m_Name: Intro Dialogue 03
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Message: "As an immediate measure, the Council decided that the birth of new children
    would be the highest priority. \nTo this end, they developed the Eve Protocol,
    where fertile men would earn benefits that include better housing, jobs with
    better hours and conditions, job stability, as well as ample subsidies for necessary
    health care, education, and other family needs.\nIn addition, the INC conglomerate
    would start buying viable sperm for the an reasonable amount of money."
